OL,3,CMan jailed after being found with meth
OL,4,Cand cocaine hidden in water bottle
OL,6,FA man has been jailed after police
OL,7,Fdiscovered drugs hidden in a converted
OL,8,Fwater bottle in Greater Manchester.
OL,10,FOfficers say it was acting as a hide
OL,11,Ffor numerous bags of methamphetamine
OL,12,Fand cocaine.
OL,14,F38 year old Christopher Sigsworth,
OL,15,Ffrom Swinton, was jailed for 27 months
OL,16,Fafter pleading guilty to the supply of
OL,17,FClass A drugs, four counts of
OL,18,Fpossession with intent to supply, and
OL,19,Fpossession of an offensive weapon.
