OL,3,CMan jailed after being found with meth
OL,4,Cand cocaine hidden in water bottle
OL,6,FHe was sentenced at Manchester Crown
OL,7,FCourt earlier in May, following an
OL,8,Finvestigation by the Salford Proactive
OL,9,FChallenger police team.
OL,11,FPC Louis Aspinall, from the team,
OL,12,Fsaid: "While he tried to hide his
OL,13,Fdrugs in a converted water bottle,
OL,14,Fultimately our Challenger team's
OL,15,Fthirst for justice outweighed his
OL,16,Fidea."
