OL,3,CMan jailed after being found with meth
OL,4,Cand cocaine hidden in water bottle
OL,6,FThe court heard how on the morning of
OL,7,F9 January 2025, officers conducted a
OL,8,Fwarrant at Sigsworth's address in
OL,9,FClifton, upon which a quantity of
OL,10,Fcocaine was discovered, which he
OL,11,Fclaimed was for personal use.
OL,13,FA further search revealed crystal
OL,14,Fmethamphetamine, a mobile phone, and
OL,15,Fother drug paraphernalia. A taser-
OL,16,Fstyle weapon was also discovered in
OL,17,Fthe property.
