OL,3,CMan jailed after being found with meth
OL,4,Cand cocaine hidden in water bottle
OL,6,FAfter being arrested, Sigsworth was
OL,7,Fbailed pending further enquiries.
OL,8,FHowever, he was spotted driving a VW
OL,9,Fin the Walkden area on 20 January,
OL,10,Fwhere he was requested to stop and
OL,11,Fsubsequently subject to a search
OL,13,FA snap bag of cocaine was discovered
OL,14,Fin addition to a water bottle. The
OL,15,Fbottle itself was acting as a hide for
OL,16,Fnumerous snap bags of methamphetamine
OL,17,Fand cocaine, having been adapted to
OL,18,Fdiscreetly hide the drugs in the
OL,19,Fmiddle.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
