OL,3,CMan jailed after being found with meth
OL,4,Cand cocaine hidden in water bottle
OL,6,FSigsworth was then arrested, charged,
OL,7,Fand remanded.
OL,9,FPC Louis Aspinall added, "Sigsworth
OL,10,Fwas involved in the supply of
OL,11,Fdangerous and illegal drugs to
OL,12,Fvulnerable people within the
OL,13,Fcommunity, and I am glad he is now
OL,14,Fbehind bars.
OL,16,F"I would urge anyone in the Salford
OL,17,Farea and who has concerns about drugs
OL,18,Fin their community to get in touch
OL,19,Fwith their local officers. We listen
OL,20,Fto all tip-offs and your intelligence
OL,21,Fwill be acted on."
